posts.post_title: T206 Germany Schaefer SGC 88 Washington for sale/trade
posts.post_content: I will entertain offers or trades although I am picky.  What I have is the highest graded Germany Schaefer-Washington card in both PSA and SGC population reports.  The card is graded an SGC 88 NM/MT 8.  Let me know what you have.  Otherwise I will likely be auctioning off sometime this year.
